node.title: Person dies after failing to resurface from river dive
node.description: One person has died in a water-related incident in Taranaki last night.
node.content:
["One person has died in a water-related incident in Taranaki last night.", "", "
Waiwhakaiho River (file picture) Photo: RNZ / Robin Martin
", "The police were called just before 7pm, after the person jumped from Te Rewa Rewa Bridge into the Waiwhakaiho River and failed to surface.", "An extensive search was undertaken, but the person was located deceased near the river mouth at 9.30pm."]
